videos.headline: New Mexico State RB zips through for TD
videos.description: RB Larry Rose jukes multiple defenders and scores 40-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: New Mexico State CB takes INT back for TD

videos.headline: Larry Rose lll big day leads New Mexico State to victory
